新細明體;color:#444444"><o:p></o:p></span></h4><h3 style="margin-left:36.0pt;background:deepskyblue"><span style="font-family:
標楷體;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:white">五、生活服務學習規劃：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></h3><ol start="1" type="1">
 <ol start="7" type="1">
